      "bullets": [
        "The Unicode Consortium rejects emoji proposals violating criteria like transient popularity, brand representation, or capability of representation via existing sequences.",
        "Managing emoji parsing requires handling Zero-Width Joiners (ZWJ) and complex grapheme clusters, impacting text rendering pipelines and storage overhead.",
        "Unicode Technical Committee (UTC) documents rejected proposals to prevent duplicate submissions and guide developers on future character encoding submissions."
      ]
